      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Affordable Fixer-Upper \u2014 Great Opportunity for the Right Buyer! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition and priced to reflect that honestly \u2014 no hidden surprises! It shows significant wear and will need some attention and repairs to get it back to its best. If you're a hands-on enthusiast, a mechanically-savvy shopper, or just need an ultra-budget-friendly option, this could be the right fit for you. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
