    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional vehicle! This car is in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it. From the gleaming, flawless exterior to the spotless, pristine interior, every inch of this vehicle has been impeccably maintained. There are no dings, no wear marks, no odors \u2014 just a stunning car that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The engine runs beautifully, all systems are in perfect working order, and the attention to detail throughout is simply remarkable. If you've been searching for the best of the best, your search ends here. Don't miss your chance to drive home something truly special!",
      "price": 46000.0,
