      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we want to give you a clear and honest picture of what you can expect. The exterior shows some signs of normal use \u2014 there are a few minor scratches and light scuffs consistent with everyday driving, but no major dents or structural damage, and the overall appearance is presentable and well-maintained. The interior is in solid shape with moderate wear on the seats and some light fading on high-contact surfaces, though everything is clean and functional. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts without issue, and all major systems are in good working order. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection, as we have nothing to hide, and we believe this vehicle represents solid value for a buyer looking for dependable transportation without paying a premium for showroom-perfect condition.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Pristine Mint Condition \u2014 A Rare Opportunity You Don't Want to Miss! \u2014 If you've been holding out for a truly exceptional vehicle, this is it! This car is in outstanding mint condition \u2014 spotless interior, flawless exterior, and mechanically sound from top to bottom. Everything works exactly as it should, and the attention to care this vehicle has received really shows. Whether you're a discerning daily driver or simply want the best, this one delivers. Come see it in person \u2014 you'll be impressed the moment you lay eyes on it!",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 buyers should go in with eyes wide open. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple dents, scratches, and paint damage that are clearly visible. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will likely require attention, and it is not in a reliable, worry-free state for daily driving without some repair investment. The interior also reflects its age and use, with worn upholstery, damaged trim, and general fatigue throughout the cabin. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises hidden in the fine print.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
