      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, glossy, and free of scratches, swirl marks, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, all trim pieces are perfectly intact, and the glass is crystal clear with no chips or cracks. The interior matches the exterior in every way \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, all surfaces are pristine, and every electronic feature, control, and comfort amenity functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and drivetrain \u2014 are in top working order. Service records are available and reflect consistent, thorough care throughout the vehicle's life. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that truly needs nothing \u2014 you can drive it away with complete confidence.",
      "price": 47000.0,
